<div class="slide active" id="slide1">
    <h2>What is Cybersecurity?</h2>
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x300/0072ff/ffffff?text=What+is+Cybersecurity" alt="What is Cybersecurity">
    <p>Cybersecurity is the practice of protecting computers, networks, and data from unauthorized access or attacks. It is essential to keep information safe in our digital world.</p>
</div>

<div class="slide" id="slide2">
    <h2>Why is Cybersecurity Important?</h2>
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x300/0072ff/ffffff?text=Importance+of+Cybersecurity" alt="Importance of Cybersecurity">
    <p>Cyberattacks can lead to stolen information, financial loss, and harm to individuals and organizations. Strong cybersecurity measures protect us from these threats.</p>
</div>

<div class="slide" id="slide3">
    <h2>Key Cybersecurity Terms</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><b>Hacker:</b> Someone who gains unauthorized access to systems.</li>
        <li><b>Malware:</b> Malicious software that harms devices or data.</li>
        <li><b>Firewall:</b> A security system that monitors and controls network traffic.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

